            "\tTask UpdateAsync(T entity, CancellationToken ct = default);",
            "\tTask DeleteAsync(${1:int} id, CancellationToken ct = default);",
            "}",
            "$0"
        ],
        "description": "Generic repository pattern interface"
    },
